### Get all animals
GET http://localhost:8080/api/animals
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single animal by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/animals/{animalId}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new animal in a specific specie
POST http://localhost:8080/api/animals/specie/{specieName}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 3,
  "weight": 10.5
}

###

### Update an existing animal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/animals/{animalId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 5,
  "weight": 12.8
}

###

### Delete an animal by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/animals/{animalId}

###

### Get all species
GET http://localhost:8080/api/species
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single specie by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/species/{specieId}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new specie
POST http://localhost:8080/api/species
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Elephant",
  "dietType": "HERBIVORE",
  "occurring": "AFRICA"
}

###

### Update an existing specie
POST http://localhost:8080/api/species/{specieId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lion",
  "dietType": "CARNIVORE",
  "occurring": "AFRICA"
}

###

### Delete a specie by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/species/{specieId}
